+- **why_include**: The most Pythonic agent framework ‚Äî Pydantic is already the validation layer under OpenAI SDK, Google ADK, Anthropic SDK, LangChain, and CrewAI. Built FastA2A (framework-agnostic A2A library). Strong partnership with Google.
